    bool
config SERIAL_BAUD
    depends on SERIAL
    int "Baud rate for serial port" if LOW_LEVEL_OPTIONS
    default 250000
    help
        Specify the baud rate of the serial port. This should be set
        to 250000. Read the FAQ before changing this value.

